                        <interp inst="t18680127-name-244" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BURROWS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman</hi> 167 <hi rend="italic">H</hi>). I took Spurdan into custody from the last witness.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Kelly's Defence</hi>. I was running from Mulberry Street to the Commercial Road when he stopped me. I asked him what he wanted, and he gave me into custody.</p>
               <p>
